1778516754528485	reckon-dev	itc:v3:AWLk8kz5M8ySZQAAAAAAQevVvre1WgAAAAEvHw		item.create	bn-34n	{"description":"Open ~/.local/share/opencode/opencode.db with SQLITE_OPEN_READONLY. Prepared statement streaming `message`\nordered by `created`. Pull tokens_input/output/reasoning/cache_read/cache_write + model_id + provider_id + session_id + id.\nUse LIMIT/OFFSET paging (1000 rows/page) to keep memory bounded on the 1.6GB DB on this machine.\ndedup_key = \"{message.id}\". Month from created (unix ts → UTC).\n","kind":"task","parent":"bn-19m","size":"m","title":"OpenCode reader: read-only SQLite stream over message rows"}	blake3:TTvoX_iHR4jP8No2ua8v8GG4RX1WNQ7nw-GMz96iE9A
